name: The Hederian Elephant

name: The Hederian Kangaroo
intro: This gold Hederian Kangaroo coin displays a jumping kangaroo, which represents speed which is one of the greatest characteristics of the Hedera network. Hederas motto's 'Hello Future' and 'Hello Speed' are displayed around the kangaroo. The design was inspired by the Kangaroo coins minted by Perth Mint Australia.
